{"tid":1341870,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"林鄭721作戰大成功","createTime":"2019-07-21T17:01:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-21T23:19:40.000Z","uid":233325,"like":26,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"5ef42b23b93da7c20a3fd5d62b539196fe9c7ab5","tid":1341870,"uid":233325,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T17:01:46.000Z","msg":"係沙田警察入商場圍堵示威者被猛烈抨擊後<br />\n政府已經無辦法叫警方警力升級<br />\n即係話721警方唔能夠再升級更大暴力清場<br />\n一個元朗鄉黑無差別打人<br />\n大眾嘅目光又會落返係黑警合作，警民衝突<br />\n今晚大家都淨係掛住講元朗白衫人嘅咁凶狠，警察幾咁無能<br />\n又再一次，香港政府成功將五大訴求、政治議題轉移焦點去警察到<br />\n冇人再記得為咩而走上街頭"},{"pid":"e45808b0d892f9b138eadb2144a892dadeba2865","tid":1341870,"uid":233325,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T17:01:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d03180ccb2777b66f60ce63182a4aedf7377ea52","tid":1341870,"uid":233325,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T17:02:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11af39328bfea9f0e5139ddcad13ccd84db97e7d","tid":1341870,"uid":23707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T17:02:20.000Z","msg":"鄉黑有無3萬人"},{"pid":"883fa9316d8371c8a3838b2b0b9e0ea09874d247","tid":1341870,"uid":31317,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T17:03:39.000Z","msg":"因為班警狗唔撚柒醒呀屌你老母！"},{"pid":"bd25fd55250c737389f0ed22373f7c3cd5dc900c","tid":1341870,"uid":135867,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T17:04:55.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://streamable.com/82ejs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstreamable.com%2F82ejs&d=YI7gf4cr217w6pzPHhIkRZMONXnVHdpXbsFGehQCOpI%3D&h=6c2eb974\" target=\"_blank\">https://streamable.com/82ejs</a><br />\n<br />\n有片 黑社會夾道歡迎何君堯<br />\n<br />\n柳俊江被毆致重傷<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kxhDKKb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkxhDKKb.jpg&h=96301925&s={S