lyTime":"2019-07-21T17:31:03.000Z","msg":"[緊急]!!!!!!請投訴西鐵008號列車!!!!!!!!<br />\n<a href=\"http://lih.kg/dmNwpT\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://lih.kg/dmNwpT</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"ea76a87754002c0ce2a513b4eac6aa8424744234","tid":1341870,"uid":99420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T23:09:58.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"fa25dc1484795012c3c4ee77541c3cd1e722436b","tid":1341870,"uid":79471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T23:17:13.000Z","msg":"上環開撚咗三十幾槍啊老友"},{"pid":"00e8bf89ba97f0a75ea434a5cc1a942ae9823c08","tid":1341870,"uid":130162,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T23:19:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1C5aC2R.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1C5aC2R.png&h=61244cc1&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}